M; clinical tests ordered: 37K - 40K.</p><p class=\"bullets_li\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 12px; padding-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-size: 17px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; float: left; width: 582px; padding-left: 14px !important; background-image: url(https://staticseekingalpha3.a.ssl.fastly.net/images/bullets/mc_bullet.png?1409587369) !important; background-position: 2px 8px !important; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat !important;\">Final 2015 results will be released next month.</p></div></div><div class=\"mc_follow_up mc_list_cont\" style=\"margin: 5px 0px 0px; padding: 1px 0px 15px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span class=\"MC_rta_bottom\" id=\"MC_rta_bottom\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; float: left; width: 640px; widows: 1;\"></span><div id=\"sticky_share_wrapper\" class=\"sticky_share_wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; position: fixed; top: 180px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.278431) 0px 0px 2px 0px; widows: 1; left: 1021px;\"><div class=\"share_widget_sticky\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; float: left; clear: none; width: 50px;\"><a href=\"http://seekingalpha.com/news/3024296-foundation-medicine-expects-over-93m-in-2015-revenues-as-much-as-120m-this-year-shares-off-6-percent?uprof=29#\" data-title=\"Foundation%20Medicine%20expects%20over%20%2493M%20in%202015%20revenues%3B%20as%20much%20as%20%24120M%20this%20year%3B%20shares%20off%206%25\" title=\"Shar